OL,3,CDown Syndrome charity faces #30,000
OL,4,Cfunding shortfall
OL,6,FA charity supporting children with
OL,7,FDown Syndrome says its future could be
OL,8,Fat risk due to funding problems.
OL,10,FSunshine and Smiles, which was set up
OL,11,F10 years ago, supports more than 180
OL,12,Ffamilies across Leeds through parent-
OL,13,Fand-baby groups, speech therapy and a
OL,14,Fcafe.
OL,16,FBut it says it is facing a #30,000
OL,17,Ffunding shortfall this financial year.
OL,19,F"Fundraising, grants and donations
OL,20,Fhave been much harder to secure this
OL,21,Fyear," it said in a statement.
