OL,4,Cfunding shortfall
OL,6,F"There is huge competition for more
OL,7,Flimited funds available, and we know
OL,8,Feveryone has been hit by the cost of
OL,9,Fliving crisis.
OL,11,F"A very important part of our ethos is
OL,12,Fthat all of our support and services
OL,13,Fremain free of charge to everyone who
OL,14,Fwants & needs to access them. We don't
OL,15,Fwant there to be any barriers to
OL,16,Fpeople getting the support they need,
OL,17,Fwhen they need it."
OL,19,FThe charity is calling for support and
OL,20,Fdonations from service users as well
OL,21,Fas encouraging people to use the cafe.
