OL,6,FCafe 21 provides employment
OL,7,Fopportunities for young adults with
OL,8,FDown Syndrome.
OL,10,FSarah Empson and her young son, Wilf,
OL,11,Fattend a singing group provided by the
OL,12,Fcharity and often visit the cafe
OL,13,Fafterwards.
OL,15,FShe said: "For us who have the younger
OL,16,Fgeneration, it's nice to think this
OL,17,Fcould be somewhere they could work in
OL,18,Fthe future. We have that aspiration
OL,19,Ffor them.''
