OL,4,Cfunding shortfall
OL,6,FService manager Ailith Harley-Roberts
OL,7,Fsaid: "Everybody should be able to
OL,8,Fhave a job. I was asking one of our
OL,9,Fyoung people what she did with her
OL,10,Fwages and she said she took her mum
OL,11,Fand dad out.
OL,13,F"I think it's something we take for
OL,14,Fgranted and people with down syndrome
OL,15,Fdon't have that afforded to them.''
